phrs.translation: 范妮梅（财富500强公司之一，总部设于美国，主要经营多种金融）

sentences.sentence: Look around in this room — all this knowledge, energy, talent, and technology. Let's get off our fannies, roll up our sleeves and get to work, passionately, in creating an almost perfect world.
sentences.translation: 看看这里，充满了知识，活力，才华和科技让我们走出冷气房，卷起袖子开始行动，带着我们的热情创造一个近乎完美的世界感谢大家。
